{"tid":351052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一出世就有幾十億遺產，其實人生重有乜嘢嘅意義？","createTime":"2017-08-07T16:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T17:38:16.000Z","uid":13378,"like":13,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f03d92e6c133f85735f1f882ad7d95b5185d10","tid":351052,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"當你有幾十億嘅時候, 你已經唔需要同人競爭，你唔需要咁努力讀書，唔需要咁努力工作，你唔需要咁努力擦鞋　<br />\n<br />\n唔通就日日喺度做愛，終日花天酒地？<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁，其實人生重有咩意義"},{"pid":"5a55adc35c9f5987e9818751f8519a401ed8488d","tid":351052,"uid":5278,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"最可笑既係<br />\n好多人既目標就係想過呢種生活"},{"pid":"06252e1ef6e6ff268e25c03c737736508f6a3284","tid":351052,"uid":79471,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"如果你係噉諗 你真係好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cd37dcdc39abfa6dac067af73512cfae180e5f","tid":351052,"uid":40010,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"其實人生有乜嘢嘅意義?<br />\n做七、八十年人<br />\n最後咩都帶唔走<br />\n風光又點<br />\n乞食又點<br />\n日日做到隻積咁<br />\n為無女無錢而煩<br />\n其實為乜"},{"pid":"7dcd25d83142b57c0ca83851371893842452b080","tid":351052,"uid":61903,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"如果一出世就已經係食物鏈既最底層<br />\n點努力都上唔到去，人生仲有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n有錢得閒咪屌下女，悶就開間公司扮下傑青<br />\n唔想做傑青又可以捐幾十皮拎個光環<br />\n大把野可以體驗，如果你覺得錢買唔到快樂一定係你用錯左方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9a6d1d79ca41aa9bd1614f47ac389bf77e04d3","tid":351052,"uid":84355,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"不如你定義下咩叫人生的意義"},{"pid":"077f56cb8f5346eb43bd6f2cdf961081cdab18ca","tid":351052,"uid":67348,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"一個人有錢都可以有佢既目標<br />\n而且有錢更加容易實踐到佢地既理想<br />\n反而係無錢先變到要日搏夜搏為果兩餐<br />\n放棄埋自己理想去做隻機械人<br />\n呢種先係最撚無意義既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bc7384c450003651f8c931b49bcdaaf8fdfe70","tid":351052,"uid":15620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你係噉諗 你真係好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7288958e762497e0801bbbbb465dfdbd0dc9497","tid":351052,"uid":67348,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"原來樓主覺得人生既意義就係日夜去同人競爭、返工做到隻狗咁<br />\n樓主眼中既人生意義都幾撚可悲下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3e9bda02055f4771df1c979cd3d106e21c3cb5","tid":351052,"uid":117993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"跟本人嘅心態就係隔籬飯香，只睇到人哋嘅快樂同自己嘅痛苦，但係唔記得自己嘅快樂"},{"pid":"bb836fe3026bf063e6751627c7d0512441317340","tid":351052,"uid":117184,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人有錢都可以有佢既目標<br />\n而且有錢更加容易實踐到佢地既理想<br />\n反而係無錢先變到要日搏夜搏為果兩餐<br />\n放棄埋自己理想去做隻機械人<br />\n呢種先係最撚無意義既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n滿足左基本物質層需求先係追求人生意義起點，體驗生命藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ef3440b08ec8e5a8a1e2ff063bdb50dc18c83b","tid":351052,"uid":22450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁樣反而會更加有興趣讀書，會覺得衰左咪衰左，大把時間再讀過。咁樣會更想尋求更多知識同埋真係輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇錢唔好去做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c822c6213d380592d9529e810e6ba3952990a9","tid":351052,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:55:17.000Z","msg":"當你自細有幾十億<br />\n你就可能唔會想呢條問題"},{"pid":"fa36e12216e18586b43e3b11022fc6ba5cb459c7","tid":351052,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"再滾大舊錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做二世祖浪費曬"},{"pid":"d5a739a83239a1414445597e0136ec32377214ad","tid":351052,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得咁樣反而會更加有興趣讀書，會覺得衰左咪衰左，大把時間再讀過。咁樣會更想尋求更多知識同埋真係輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇錢唔好去做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你答我你自己做咩要讀書？"},{"pid":"f87a9023f901df5e12f66db40d152fa65091e6d2","tid":351052,"uid":22302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:55:42.000Z","msg":"我唔直接答你，我用例子答你<br />\n以前（19世紀前）好多科學家都係父幹撚"},{"pid":"ae70bdd458f5630d6d9740c3f8df9063ff691b31","tid":351052,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"有無諗過其實你連基因都輸埋俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabb6621db3a2b35a54491944ad0d238e7dfbab1","tid":351052,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣反而會更加有興趣讀書</span>，會覺得衰左咪衰左，大把時間再讀過。咁樣會更想尋求更多知識同埋真係輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇錢唔好去做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔一定，要有某d事件觸發到劇情先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過香港冇錢唔好諗做研究真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非係天才 否則至少都要老豆老母供得起你讀成個大學 唔使你做pt既程度"},{"pid":"1a5cdf9addab965e4700a3da0af135c24c5e9a8f","tid":351052,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"不過掉返轉講 你一出世都冇遺產啦 你既人生咪又係冇意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43448530e3f542b9561faaa007b91a3c943ed04","tid":351052,"uid":23021,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"人地係創造mode minecraft<br />\n你係生存mode"},{"pid":"5413a285a945c6ec64f845d953e37d1e0838c9ea","tid":351052,"uid":67864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"樓主真可悲"},{"pid":"44d2af0d62360372685218549dc94d39e2032664","tid":351052,"uid":48830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"調轉講唔通讀書返工先係人生嘅意義咩<br />\n窮&gt;返工搵錢養自己&gt;人生無意義<br />\n有錢&gt;唔洗搵錢都養到自己&gt;人生都係無意義<br />\n只可以話搵錢係現今社會99%嘅人嘅目標掛<br />\n但我唔認同賺錢係我生存嘅意義<br />\n但係講到尾都唔知自己人生嘅意義係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d797ae3dc9cc6be476a54c808ae736f3899faa","tid":351052,"uid":57073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"有幾十億嘅時候<br />\n只有兩個方向<br />\n1. 好似誠哥咁 玩數字遊戲 追求獲勝嘅feel<br />\n2. 用錢破壞其他人心血"},{"pid":"c0a9e52c3bccce4f2fed73ceb3620875e33f823c","tid":351052,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得咁樣反而會更加有興趣讀書，會覺得衰左咪衰左，大把時間再讀過。咁樣會更想尋求更多知識同埋真係輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇錢唔好去做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你答我你自己做咩要讀書？</blockquote><br />\n如果有錢我想做研究新醫療科技，幫助世人。<br />\n名留青史其1， 其2 係我真心想幫下"},{"pid":"39f60f5b389abce4fd35f34ade8bb9c9e24d159e","tid":351052,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾樓主"},{"pid":"4a6316f92fbf5df01c1b4110dd274c75d11dc5b1","tid":351052,"uid":13378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非你係呢個世界最頂尖1%嘅人，如果唔係你嘅人生係無意義，70億人，多你一個唔多，少你一個唔少<br />\n<br />\n或者只有抑鬱症病人先能夠體驗人生真正嘅意義，<br />\n除咗為咗人類可以不斷咁繁殖之外根本再冇其他意義"},{"pid":"3d9b9d01a