0cee2e9ba","tid":351052,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>垃圾樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非你係呢個世界最頂尖1%嘅人，如果唔係你嘅人生係無意義，70億人，多你一個唔多，少你一個唔少<br />\n<br />\n或者只有抑鬱症病人先能夠體驗人生真正嘅意義，<br />\n除咗為咗人類可以不斷咁繁殖之外根本再冇其他意義</blockquote><br />\n客觀角度嚟講 人生根本唔存在意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你有幾多錢<br />\n&quot;真正嘅意義&quot;本身就係偽命題<br />\n社會地位同物質喺多數眼中可能priority好高<br />\n但永遠唔會去到&quot;意義&quot;嘅地步"},{"pid":"3ae6766492980d4753efa11ff39ed15069c52b5b","tid":351052,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得咁樣反而會更加有興趣讀書，會覺得衰左咪衰左，大把時間再讀過。咁樣會更想尋求更多知識同埋真係輕鬆好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港冇錢唔好去做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你答我你自己做咩要讀書？</blockquote><br />\n所以你覺得冇人鍾意讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33382ad63390fd942056c8ab41fe3fe53d10e81","tid":351052,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:12:48.000Z","msg":"你有幾十億嗰陣就唔會諗呢啲on9問題"},{"pid":"29f93b1375a8ae55321ef8786f04f0b84e52738f","tid":351052,"uid":21392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:14:36.000Z","msg":"你嘅人生得做愛同錢<br />\n好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae577e6bffe42d4e6b7b62002a6ae26d135f6c2","tid":351052,"uid":117958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"樓主認真大鄉里，你係咪唔知洗錢都係一門學問？學消費分分鐘連degree都有得讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318b00499de3603d51906db0f1413facc5d8132d","tid":351052,"uid":18720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:19:37.000Z","msg":"你呢啲係典型既窮撚基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可想而知即使真係天降橫財比你 都係改變唔到你人生<br />\n有錢冇錢都可以活出人生既意義<br />\n如果你份工朝九晚五而冇life可言咁係你人生苦燥<br />\n如果你朝九晚九做到狗咁都儲唔到錢 你不如反省下點解咁撚廢要做份咁既閪工 有冇得做啲野黎make a change"},{"pid":"83b2cf6f3b992af7096dc01cea1426edbbcc6801","tid":351052,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"到時你就會想買幾億既別墅而唔係幾百萬既狗聖3"},{"pid":"a328705fdb9673e7bc95ae853f87998264aaa397","tid":351052,"uid":68445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到時你就會想買幾億既別墅而唔係幾百萬既狗屋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"aa57433e9b4cdb143fd75eb6bd3674fddd82a53b","tid":351052,"uid":117958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢啲係典型既窮撚基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可想而知即使真係天降橫財比你 都係改變唔到你人生<br />\n有錢冇錢都可以活出人生既意義<br />\n如果你份工朝九晚五而冇life可言咁係你人生苦燥<br />\n如果你朝九晚九做到狗咁都儲唔到錢 你不如反省下點解咁撚廢要做份咁既閪工 有冇得做啲野黎make a change</blockquote><br />\n賤骨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912219860e246b2ec1bb7e4fbb1e881225db120f","tid":351052,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:25:16.000Z","msg":"個意義好簡單<br />\n就係唔好成日望住人地<br />\n做返你自己"},{"pid":"58085b240169fb39b57f121bcb3d35633242cec3","tid":351052,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:25:42.000Z","msg":"為開心，為舒服囉<br />\n做所有野都係架啦"},{"pid":"0f00e3c1ac60ca0a08bc07b8dc373290817485e0","tid":351052,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:26:35.000Z","msg":"原來發左達，人生就冇意義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4975d4a4c7ced4de789ab4681689d2dea9bd73","tid":351052,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"你日日打工又好有意義？"},{"pid":"d392ef932e1de1719585e7b9309566e28c2febc2","tid":351052,"uid":7374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:30:28.000Z","msg":"