ormal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遺產都有用盡嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾十億嘅話點洗得唒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗錢有幾難"},{"pid":"247028ee936f30c6e019d6cc10228e2106ee9f8d","tid":351052,"uid":84855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比我就追自己夢想，做自己想做嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後翻工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遺產都有用盡嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾十億嘅話點洗得唒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗錢有幾難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一億都可以好快洗唒，但幾十億嘅話根本你可能啲利息都已經夠用<br />\n<br />\n就算買飛機買遊艇都係講緊幾億內已經買倒嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868cbc46225e2ec6a3bb3b958d598cfae700dfa6","tid":351052,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"日日返工做奴好有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d31fa0f1f1a3a1ae93aa7600c9b304d0ed11a58","tid":351052,"uid":58503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你有幾十億嘅時候, 你已經唔需要同人競爭，你唔需要咁努力讀書，唔需要咁努力工作，你唔需要咁努力擦鞋　<br />\n<br />\n唔通就日日喺度做愛，終日花天酒地？<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁，其實人生重有咩意義</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你諗下d有幾百億既有錢佬，點解佢地重要賺錢，你就會知有錢唔等於人生無意義。"},{"pid":"5b917b53ec6dda517d235018d8ab4f6f07b6cfe8","tid":351052,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"樓主好俗氣冇主見<br />\n淨係識迎合社會（低層）